This file is a flag. It exists with a certain name.

If it is named motion_on - the motion script will start
If it is named motion_off - the motion script will not start
Actually, if it is not named motion_on - the motion script will not start.

We do this in case we need to do some debugging. We can just change the name of the file and reboot, then start manually.

Motion is started in crontab using the @reboot command. It sleeps before starting, giving you a minute to change the name of this file.
